reviews.review:
[h1] What are you waiting for? [/h1] 

Absolute buy-and-replay puzzle game!

The story is intriguing and unexpected;
The universe is mysterious;
The pace and level design are excellent;
The dialog is unforgettable;
The voice acting is unique.

In fact I wish that I was about to press [b]Play[/b] for the first time as I write this review.
This game does not age a bit, it still feels fresh and compelling even after several playthroughs.
I'd recommend it without hesitation.
